paragraph.content:
Exempt from all direct taxes; it is understood, however, that the specialized
                agencies will not claim exemption from taxes which are, in fact, no more than
                charges for public utility services;

Immunity from personal arrest or detention and from seizure of their personal
                baggage, and in respect of words spoken or written and all acts done by them in
                their official capacity, immunity from legal process of every kind;

Enjoy the same exemptions from taxation in respect of the salaries and
                emoluments paid to them by the specialized agencies and on the same conditions as
                are enjoyed by officials of the United Nations;
